body_html: For anyone else who is running into the same issue, I was also having similar problems when trying to import tensorflow on notebook via jupyter. The modules were installed using conda. After spending two days on it without any success (kept getting the same, no module any_pb2/contrib), it was obvious it was a notebook problem and not tensorflow related since I could import tensorflow from python shell. So I decided to switch back to vanilla python and installed everything manually (tensorflow via pip & got rid of jupyter & installed ipython instead) and now I am able to import tensorflow from my ipython notebook.
